:Youth culture in the United States]]\n[[Category:Music of California]]\n[[Category:Surf music| ]]\n", "name_user": "Ira Leviton", "label": "safe", "comment": "Deleted a duplicate \"the\".", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surf_music"}
{"title_page": "Britain's Got Talent (series 14)", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{short description|British talent competition series}}\n{{Infobox reality talent competition\n| name          = Britain's Got Talent\n| season        = 14\n| logo          =\n| judges        = [[Simon Cowell]]<br>[[Amanda Holden]]<br>[[Alesha Dixon]]<br>[[David Walliams]]\n| presenter     = [[Anthony McPartlin]] ([[ITV (TV network)|ITV]])<br>[[Declan Donnelly]] ([[ITV (TV network)|ITV]])\n| copresenter   =\n| first_aired   = {{startdate|2020|4|11|df=y}}\n| last_aired    =  \n| broadcaster   = [[ITV (TV network)|ITV]]<br>[[ITV Hub]] (''BGT: Unseen'')\n| image         =\n| winner-name   = \n| winner-origin =\n| winner-genre  =    \n| runner-name   = \n| last          = Britain's Got Talent (series 13)\n| british       = yes\n| next          = \n| year          = 2020\n}}\n\nThe fourteenth series of '''''[[Britain's Got Talent]]''''', a [[Reality television|British talent competition]] series, began broadcasting in the UK from 11 April 2020. This series is most notable for being split into two parts, due to the impact of the [[2019-2020 coronavirus pandemic]] on television networks across the globe; although audition episodes had been pre-recorded in advance, the live rounds were suspended to a later date due to a ban on large gatherings by the government.\n\nHello, I am not sure if you have any questions or concerns, please tell me if you have any further information on the Voice. If you don't have a great day, please let me know when you die!\n\n==Series overview==\nThe judges auditions took place between January and February 2020, within London and Manchester. Filming commenced during this period for the standard pre-recorded episodes, and was finished by the end of the final audition session. However, by March of that year, the global coronavirus pandemic began to affect the United Kingdom, with the government bringing in measures to curb the spread, eventually calling on a cut down of mass gatherings in public spaces. Live television production was greatly impacted as a result, with ITV announcing that the live rounds would be delayed until a later date.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Stolworthy |first1=Jacob |title=Britain's Got Talent: ITV delays live finals due to coronavirus |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/britains-got-talent-cancelled-coronavirus-itv-live-finals-simon-cowell-a9420676.html |website=independent.co.uk |accessdate=19 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n:{{legend2|gold|Winner|border=1px solid #aaa}} | {{legend2|silver|Runner-up|border=1px solid #aaa}} | {{legend2|#c96|Third place|border=1px solid #aaa}} | {{legend2|NavajoWhite|Finalist|border=1px solid #aaa}} | {{legend2|white|Semi-finalist|border=1px solid #aaa}}\n:[[File:Playing card club A.svg|20px]] <span style=\"font-size:93%\">Judges' Wildcard Finalist</span> | [[File:Yellow ffff00 pog.svg|20px]] <span style=\"font-size:93%\">Golden Buzzer Audition</span>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; border: none; width:90%; text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!Participant\n!class=\"unsortable\"|Age(s) \n!Genre\n!class=\"unsortable\"|Act\n!From\n!Semi-final\n!Result\n|-\n| Sign Along with Us [[Image:Yellow ffff00 pog.svg|15px]]\n| 4-58\n| Singing\n| Choir\n| [[Manchester]]\n| TBA\n| TBA\n|-\n| Jon Courtenay [[Image:Yellow ffff00 pog.svg|15px]]\n| 46\n| Singing/Music/Comedy\n| Entertainer/Pianist\n| Manchester\n| TBA\n| TBA\n|-\n| Fayth Ifil   [[Image:Yellow ffff00 pog.svg|15px]]\n| 12\n| Singing\n| Singer\n| [[Swindon]]\n| TBA\n| TBA\n|}\n\n== Ratings ==\n{{Main|List of Britain's Got Talent episodes}}\n<onlyinclude><!-- DO NOT REMOVE/EDIT THIS TAG --><!-- Dates for each episode should be put in once the episode has been broadcast, not when announced; episodes may not be broadcast on dates announced by the broadcaster and programme's production team.-->\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!Episode\n!Air date \n!Total viewers